metadata.name: Lan And Chill
metadata.description:
"It's the early 2000's and you and your friends are hanging out on a Saturday night planing to LAN together and just have a chill, its the days where the internet was not easy accessible and online gaming was still not popular, these LAN nights brought friends together."

"You will always get the friend who never gets cold, who is always hungry and the friend who always tag along with her boyfriend, the friend that just wanna talk about games and how much he loves it and the cool chick who is always gaming with the bro's and then there is the introvert who are not much for talking but just want to play his favorite game"
